    <item>
      <title>特朗普任命“Sharpiegate”科学家领导美国气象局</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/trump-taps-sharpiegate-scientist-to-lead-us-weather-agency</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普政府已任命因“夏普门”飓风预报争议相关不当行为而受到指控的科学家尼尔雅各布斯 (Neil Jacobs) 领导负责监督美国政府天气预报和气候研究的机构。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/trump-taps-sharpiegate-scientist-to-lead-us-weather-agency</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 15:31:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>罗伯特·肯尼迪 (RFK Jr.) 获得参议院委员会批准，将为卫生与公众服务部进行全面投票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/rfk-jr-clears-senate-committee-heads-to-full-vote-to-lead-hhs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗伯特·F·肯尼迪 (Robert F. Kennedy Jr.) 是唐纳德·特朗普总统提名的美国卫生与公众服务部部长，在经过两次艰难的听证会后，他获得了参议院财政委员会的认可。他的提名现在将提交参议院全体投票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/rfk-jr-clears-senate-committee-heads-to-full-vote-to-lead-hhs</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 15:28:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>万斯将出席巴黎人工智能峰会，强调特朗普的优先事项</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/vance-to-attend-ai-summit-in-paris-highlighting-trump-priority</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，美国副总统 JD Vance 将于下周出席巴黎人工智能峰会，此行将凸显美国政府对这一快速发展行业的关注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/vance-to-attend-ai-summit-in-paris-highlighting-trump-priority</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 15:13:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴拿马考虑取消与香港公司的港口交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/panama-said-to-mull-canceling-port-deal-with-hong-kong-firm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，巴拿马正在考虑是否取消与运营巴拿马运河附近港口的香港公司的合同，此举可能是为了化解唐纳德·特朗普总统关于对抗中国在这条关键水道周围影响力的威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/panama-said-to-mull-canceling-port-deal-with-hong-kong-firm</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 15:01:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普制定加密货币友好议程，推动稳定币立法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/new-stablecoin-bill-pushed-as-trump-sets-crypto-friendly-agenda</link>
      <description><![CDATA[参议员比尔·哈格蒂将于周二提出立法，为稳定币建立一个框架，这是共和党为制定加密友好型指导方针的最新举措，而加密行业是唐纳德·特朗普总统的优先事项。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/new-stablecoin-bill-pushed-as-trump-sets-crypto-friendly-agenda</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 14:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克和阿克曼离职后，特拉华州著名的商业法庭受到州长的严厉审视</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/as-musk-and-ackman-snub-delaware-governor-looks-hard-at-court</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一个多世纪以来，特拉华州一直拥有美国首屈一指的商业法庭，是大多数财富 500 强公司和美国最大公司诉讼的合法审理地。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/as-musk-and-ackman-snub-delaware-governor-looks-hard-at-court</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 14:00:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平对特朗普关税的回应表明中国将面临更多损失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/xi-s-careful-reply-to-trump-tariffs-shows-china-has-more-to-lose</link>
      <description><![CDATA[最新一轮中美贸易战的首轮攻势明确表明，习近平采取了比唐纳德·特朗普第一任期期间更为谨慎的态度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/xi-s-careful-reply-to-trump-tariffs-shows-china-has-more-to-lose</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 12:01:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>内塔尼亚胡准备与特朗普会面，权力仍未稳固</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/netanyahu-readies-trump-white-house-meeting-with-gaza-ceasefire-at-crucial-stage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普和本杰明·内塔尼亚胡周二的会谈将决定以色列与哈马斯战争的进程，并可能决定总理继续执政的能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/netanyahu-readies-trump-white-house-meeting-with-gaza-ceasefire-at-crucial-stage</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 07:02:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普任命宽带扩张计划批评者监督该计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/trump-to-tap-critic-of-biden-broadband-plan-to-oversee-program</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据三位知情人士透露，特朗普政府选择了前总统乔·拜登 425 亿美元宽带融资计划的反对者来监督该计划，这使其方向受到质疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/trump-to-tap-critic-of-biden-broadband-plan-to-oversee-program</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 01:49:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法官拒绝特朗普驳回资金冻结诉讼请求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/judge-extends-block-of-trump-funding-freeze-plan-in-second-delay</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名法官表示，特朗普政府“没有给出任何理由”在进行意识形态审查前不到 24 小时就切断可能高达数万亿美元的联邦拨款、贷款和其他财政援助。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/judge-extends-block-of-trump-funding-freeze-plan-in-second-delay</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 22:44:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
